(288, 92, 'testimonial_content', 'We first bought two rugs from Tariq over a decade ago. At that time we found him extremely knowledgeable and helpful. The rugs are high quality and remain beautiful. Today we bought our third rug from Tariq and had the same pleasant, professional experience. This shop was the only place we looked and, with Tariq\'s guidance, we found exactly what we wanted. Excellent service and fair prices. Thank you!'),
