(295, 97, 'testimonial_content', 'GORG IS GREAT. Tariq and staff are the most professional, knowledgeable, accommodating and pleasant to work with. The products are fabulous whether from the amazing collection he has or custom \r\nmade. We have worked with him for years and will continue when\r\never our design needs call for excellent product and cleaning. \r\nThey always go above and beyond. Highly recommend you try them \r\nand see for yourself'),
