(309, 99, 'testimonial_content', 'The Archdiocese of Miami is hosting a gala later this year in honor of its 60th Anniversary. We have been looking for companies in all fields to donate items for our auction. One of those companies, The Grand Oriental Rug Gallery, donated the most beautiful area rug. The rug’s earth tone will blend right in with any style home. Whoever wins this bid will be quite satisfied.  The staff was very friendly and easy to work with. We highly recommend their products and look forward to working with them in the future'),
