(625, 1, '2019-12-15 17:10:53', '2019-12-15 17:10:53', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Decorating your living space with Oriental rugs is a means of adding your touch of individuality and creativity to each room, in ways furniture never could.<br>Just because a rug LOOKS clean doesn’t mean that it IS. One of the most overlooked places may just be underneath you.<br>Our ability to recognize your carpet’s fibers and dyes, coupled with the experience and equipment to care for them properly, allows us to revive your rug’s natural colors and beauty.<br>Did you know? [state fact?] Wool rugs can hold several pounds of dirt and soil before they even begin to look ‘dirty’. In fact loose grit and soil are abrasive and will contribute to the degradation of your rug. Vacuuming is beneficial on the surface and for maintenance, but is no substitute for professional cleaning.<br>A crucial aspect of your rug’s maintenance is a professional rug cleaning at least once a year for high trafficked areas, and for less-trafficked areas, every two to three years.<br>Getting rid of these unseen dust mites is possible with professional cleaning. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/7.jpg\",\"id\":655} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim-NaN has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/7.jpg)\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"placeholder\":\"Write title…\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">Doral</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Every step in the rug washing process is carefully tailored to fit your carpet’s unique needs. This includes choosing a particular method for washing. Maintenance of your rug prevents the onset of mold, dust mites or particle pollutants. We offer amazing and professional carpet cleaning services in Doral to ensure prolonged life of your carpet as well as healthy indoor living.</li><li>A neglected carpet can also be a cause behind triggering allergies and health issues. This can be detrimental to children, pets, those sensitive to allergens, and the overall environment.</li><li>All carpets can benefit from a cleaning of some sort.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As dedicated rug cleaners in Doral, your satisfaction is our top priority. We strive to assure thorough cleaning and outstanding results, bringing a renewed ambience to your living space. With our advanced cleaning techniques and state of the art location, we deliver timely services at an affordable price. Periodic cleaning assures a good look to your rug, and we promise to deliver amazing results.<br>We offer pick-up and delivery service Monday through Saturday. Simply call 305 442 4500 Or 305 490 1936<br>Doral is a growing city located in north-central Miami. Located near Miami International Airport and twelve miles from the Miami CBD, Doral boasts an up-and-coming urban center and several new development projects. Doral is home to the largest expatriate Venezuelan community, and boasts delicious restaurants, a large logistics industry, several corporate office headquarters, and the famous golf course and spa, from which Doral derives its name.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Doral', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'doral', '', '', '2019-12-22 04:13:41', '2019-12-22 04:13:41', '', 0, 'http://ec2-13-59-55-3.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/?post_type=service-areas&#038;p=625', 0, 'service-areas', '', 0),
(626, 1, '2019-12-15 17:11:46', '2019-12-15 17:11:46', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> A carpet has been known to us since the good golden days and is a beautifully woven natural fibres, used to cover the floor. It is one of the best things to be used to protect the flooring, enhance the beauty of the room and as well ensure insulation of the room environment. Carpets or rugs often used interchangeably are known to offer a good feel, which is often soft and provides warmth to the feet. Beauty and life of your carpet depends on the care and maintenance it receives. It is not an exaggeration, and this is the reason behind increased&nbsp;<strong>carpet cleaning services Palmetto Bay.</strong><br>Proper cleaning will not only enhance the beauty of the carpet but will also enhance its lifespan. A clean carpet stretched within the room indicates clean and fresh air circulating indoor. But ensuring to have a clean carpet and maintaining it throughout is the key. This article contains information about caring for a carpet or a rug as followed by the<strong>&nbsp;rug cleaner’s palmetto bay.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1Adownload-1.jpg\",\"id\":705} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim-NaN has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(http://ec2-3-134-86-175.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1Adownload-1.jpg)\"><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"placeholder\":\"Write title…\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">Palmetto Bay</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Tips for caring a carpet:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is often said that carpet cleaning and maintenance takes a toll on the individual doing it. However, the beauty of the carpet can be restored only through proper maintenance. It could be any kind of carpet say an&nbsp;<strong>Oriental rug.</strong>&nbsp;caring for carpet is the key. Here are few tips on caring for the carpet from the experts offering&nbsp;<strong>Carpet Cleaning Services Palmetto Bay.</strong>&nbsp;They include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Vacuum:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Carpets need to be vacuumed once in a week depending upon their usage. It is said that frequency of vacuuming the carpets can have an impact on their lifespan. If the carpets are laid wall to wall, cleaning can be made easier by dividing the carpets into quadrants and cleaned accordingly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Spots and spills should be checked:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Make sure to clean the spots and spills as soon as you notice them. Get required cleaning information and instructions from the manufacturer so as to clean these spills effectively and maintain the life of the carpet.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Professional help can do:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Take the help of professionals like the Rug Cleaners Palmetto Bay for every 6 to 12 months so as to clean the carpets and remove any sort of embedded dirt and grime.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Prevention is the best option:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One can try using mats outside the door, or remove shoes outside, even before entering the house to prevent outside dust entering into the house and then onto the carpets.One of the enemies of your rugs is moths. They do their damage in the larval stage when, they eat tracks in the wool rugs leaving behind a web-like material. So the rug that is regularly walked on and vacuumed regularly is hardly at the risk at all, except parts of it that may be under a never -disturbed area of rug.We offer pick-up and delivery service Monday through Saturday. Simply call 305 442 4500 Or 305 490 1936.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Palmetto Bay', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'palmetto-bay', '', '', '2019-12-22 04:13:37', '2019-12-22 04:13:37', '', 0, 'http://ec2-13-59-55-3.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/?post_type=service-areas&#038;p=626', 0, 'service-areas', '', 0),
