(54, 54, 'product_cat', '<h2>Tribal Rugs. Tribal Area Rugs.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block-heading-text\">Nomadic woven far from the carpet weaving centers, tribal rugs bring a feeling of ingenuity and nature, these generations-old techniques and designs, uninfluenced by the market demand or influx of modernity.</div>', 0, 1),
